## 5. `src/routes/_authed/workspace/new.tsx` — submission and state

**State:** `workspaceType` (`TenantType`, default `"org"`), `name`, `formError`, `isCreating`.

**Submit handler:**

- `preventDefault`, reads `FormData` from `event.currentTarget`, gets `name`, trims; falls back to `name` state if needed; **returns early if empty** (no error set in that path).
- Clears `formError`, sets `isCreating` true.
- Calls **`createTenantFn({ data: { name: trimmed, tenantType: workspaceType } })`**.
- On success: **`router.invalidate()`**, then **`navigate({ to: "/" })`**.
- On failure: sets **`formError`** to a fixed string.
- **`finally`**: `setIsCreating(false)`.

**Form markup:** `method="post"` `onSubmit={handleSubmit}`; controlled `Input` `id="workspace-name"` `name="name"` `value={name}` `onChange` updates state; workspace type is **`type="button"`** buttons updating `workspaceType` (not in `FormData`); submit button **`disabled={isCreating || !name.trim()}`**.

```76:103:/Users/duhl/git/ui/apps/org-next/src/routes/_authed/workspace/new.tsx
  const handleSubmit = async (event: React.SubmitEvent<HTMLFormElement>) => {
    event.preventDefault();
    const formData = new FormData(event.currentTarget);
    const nameField = formData.get("name");
    const fromForm = typeof nameField === "string" ? nameField.trim() : "";
    const trimmed = fromForm || name.trim();
    if (!trimmed) {
      return;
    }

    setFormError(null);
    setIsCreating(true);

    try {
      await createTenantFn({
        data: {
          name: trimmed,
          tenantType: workspaceType,
        },
      });
      await router.invalidate();
      await navigate({ to: "/" });
    } catch {
      setFormError("Could not create your workspace. Please try again.");
    } finally {
      setIsCreating(false);
    }
  };
```

